FBIS4-8597 "dreeu073_i_94005" FBIS-EEU-94-073 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA UNHCR Officials `Under House Arrest' UNHCR Officials `Under House Arrest' LD1504133794 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in English 1203 GMT 15 Apr 94 LD1504133794 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network English BFN [Text] At least eight UN High Commission for Refugees officials are being held under house arrest in Serb-held Bosnian territory, according to a spokesman in Zagreb, Peter Kessler. He said that the organization's staff had been instructed to remain in their offices and added that a similar restriction had been enforced in Banja Luka for several days.
